        "collapsible_tab_CdRjGG": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "heading": "Usage Instructions",
            "content": "<p>Step 1: Apply the <strong>scrub</strong> on dry skin, massage gently, then rinse and pat dry.<br/>Step 2: On damp skin, apply a generous layer of the <strong>shaving gel</strong> and shave using a clean, sharp razor. Rinse thoroughly.<br/>Step 3: On clean, dry skin, apply the <strong>aftershave oil</strong> and allow it to fully absorb.</p><p>Use during every shaving session for best results.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_LNMEj6": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What's Included",
            "content": "<p><strong>Prep – Peach Polish Booty Scrub</strong><br/>Exfoliates and clears pores for a smoother, closer shave. Use before every shave to buff away dead skin and reduce the chance of ingrowns.</p><p><strong>Protect – Skin Smoother Shaving Gel</strong><br/>A translucent, cushiony gel that allows you to see what you're doing while shaving. It creates a silky barrier to help prevent cuts, razor burn, and irritation.</p><p><strong>Restore – Aftershave Oil</strong><br/>Calms and moisturizes the skin post-shave while helping prevent redness and ingrown hairs. Absorbs quickly and leaves skin feeling soft, not greasy.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_p9YYL3": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "heart",
            "heading": "FAQs",
            "content": "<p><strong>Is this kit suitable for sensitive skin?</strong><br/>Yes—each product is formulated with gentle, nourishing ingredients, making it safe for even the most sensitive areas.</p><p><strong>How does this kit help prevent shave bumps and ingrown hairs?</strong><br/>The scrub clears buildup and unclogs pores, the gel cushions the skin to prevent irritation, and the aftershave oil soothes and hydrates to reduce inflammation and ingrowns.</p><p><strong>How often should I use the products?</strong><br/>Use the full 3-step routine every time you shave. For smoother skin long-term, exfoliate 2–3 times a week and apply the oil daily—even on non-shaving days.</p><p><strong>Any special tips?</strong><br/>Consistency is key. Stick to the routine, and always shave with a clean, sharp razor. Your skin will thank you.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "keep_open": false
          }
        },
